# VHS Tape: Keel Workflow Demo
# Run: vhs docs/demo/demo.tape

Output docs/demo/keel-workflow.gif
Output docs/demo/keel-workflow.mp4

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 0ms

Hide
Type "bash docs/demo/demo-workflow.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 45s
